This Project is to track a colored object.

Before running it, make sure you have install OpenCV and MMAL library.

Color is define in function "GetThresholdedImage" in camcv_vid0.c. Blue is currently define. 

To track other color, you have to find its ranges in HSV color space using the open source software "ColorWheelHSV" 
download: https://app.box.com/s/f800b648b66e151e2866 (for Win OS only).
